  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Establishes the interagency elder justice task force consisting of representatives of state agencies whose work involves elder justice to create greater collaboration and develop overarching strategies, systems, and programs with a goal of protecting older adults from abuse and mistreatment."
    }
